{"tid":1441084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯外交部批評外國勢力干預香港事務，目的是摧毀中俄關係 並指責CIA干涉全世界","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:08:15.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ae89426dafb52d67c1a7931209f076e5987b81b1","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/362390/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%BF%84%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E5%A4%96%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99-%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E6%91%A7%E6%AF%80%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%84%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F362390%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258B%2599-%25E6%2597%25A8%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2591%25A7%25E6%25AF%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=263c7815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/362390/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%BF%84%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E5%A4%96%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99-%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E6%91%A7%E6%AF%80%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%84%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外交部發言人扎哈羅娃（Maria Zakharova）談及8月9日中國外交部發言人華春瑩就美國涉港言論的相關表態。扎哈羅娃表示，外國勢力干預香港事務，目的是摧毀中俄關係。<br />\n<br />\n扎哈羅娃說：「我們聽到中國領導層發出聲明，指責一些西方情報機構，尤其是美國情報機構代表干預中國內部事務。（他們）不僅僅是在對全世界進行干涉，還具體參與那些我們在香港看到的騷亂。」她說，這些外國勢力干預，對中俄關係有破壞性的影響。<br />\n<br />\n扎哈羅娃補充說，俄方對此「嚴正看待」，並認為與中國通過相關部門交換類似數據的做法是正確及有用的。她說她與中國相關部門人士快將討論有關議題。"},{"pid":"e56fe8628472207547f1ff049068b740a0483d91","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f59980a5f9f8f817271b8563e5a858e867d3122","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1856d77ebaf9892592c4269d45f10862342b7d","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba5db6a5fd40fa85a34602e639804b783809139","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95588eb20f0a727a0db80de9f2626d7368489278","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d902bc0205bd5622848f2815cd619459c2a5c07e","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7ad0bbb28f39298f1bc07482b57b074220f325","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dd5a95acc78dd890aa13d5547e674df5640891","tid":1441084,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}